  "title": "Logistics Customer Support Executive(Central)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle customer inquiries via phone and email professionally and promptly</li><li>Coordinate with internal logistics and operations teams</li><li>Provide shipment updates and resolve issues efficiently</li><li>Maintain accurate documentation and records</li><li>Build and maintain strong customer relationships</li><li>Update and maintain work task management (Monday.com)</li><li>Assist in general administrative and support tasks when needed</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min 2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Prior experience in customer service in logistics </li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong>.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to\nsafeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection\nAct (PDPA). </p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.\n</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Chen Shih Ying</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25126521</p>",
